welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Kendale Lakes! Get ready to experience the charm of this quaint city known for its picturesque lakes and friendly locals. Enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all the hidden gems it has to offer."

terminals.name: Central Terminal

terminals.name: South Terminal

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Opa Locka Airport is a small but modern facility, offering a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Opa Locka Airport is reserved for private and charter flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Fort Lauderdale Executive Airport serves as the primary hub for commercial and private aviation.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Fort Lauderdale Executive Airport is primarily used for private and corporate aviation.

wifi.note: Complimentary Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: This terminal primarily serves domestic flights and is home to Southwest Airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: This terminal serves both domestic and international flights and is home to Delta Air Lines and Air Canada.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights and is home to JetBlue and Spirit Airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 4
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights and is home to American Airlines, United Airlines, and Allegiant Air.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport. Premium options are also available for purchase.
